Package: quizify
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Quizes for Rmarkdown in RStudio
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joshua R. Goldstein
Maintainer: Joshua R. Goldstein <josh.goldstein@berkeley.edu>
Description: Processes an Rmarkdown notebook with quiz questions and answers 
    into an interactive document with feedback from answers that can be used 
    in Rstudio. Requires a specific syntax for the quiz answers. Produces an
    Rmarkdown document that is interactive.
   
URL: http://github.com/josh-goldstein-git/quizify
BugReports: http://github.com/josh-goldstein-git/quizify/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: base64enc
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
